{"tid":1115792,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[波子奧運] Marblelympics 2019 將於4月20號凌晨3點開賽 賽事討論","createTime":"2019-04-19T12:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T05:07:26.000Z","uid":14404,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89f9940a5fd955a97aa2ccb63d26ede09ef15b5e","tid":1115792,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQNCg4s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQNCg4s.jpg&h=ff41fbf9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今屆主辦隊伍 : </span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Oceanics</span></span><br />\n參賽隊伍包括 (共16隊) :<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7ADL18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7ADL18.jpg&h=fac48974&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nJelle's Marble Runs YouTube Channel :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYJdpnjuSWVOLgGT9fIzL0g/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCYJdpnjuSWVOLgGT9fIzL0g%2Ffeatured&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=85ddcc8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYJdpnjuSWVOLgGT9fIzL0g/featured</a><br />\n今屆總共有16項競賽，已知賽程有 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[因為時差關係所以香港時間可能會遲一日]</span><br />\n19/4   開幕禮 + Underwater Race<br />\n23/4   Funnel Spinning<br />\n26/4   Balancing<br />\n30/4   Gravitrax&reg; Slalom<br />\n...<br />\n重溫 :<br />\n2019 Marblelympics 資格賽 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O2AbcCbyJ2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO2AbcCbyJ2U&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=3d1d870b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O2AbcCbyJ2U</a><br />\n2019 Marblelympics 友誼賽 :<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[主辦隊伍(上屆第3) + 上屆1-4名自動獲得今屆參賽權]</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssIYDJRGDeU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DssIYDJRGDeU&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1d92097c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssIYDJRGDeU</a>"},{"pid":"4e16bc72993d70642ea054b714d8bb34bb65e33d","tid":1115792,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:26:31.000Z","msg":"吹水台好易沉底<br />\n重開希望有人一齊睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b99ec8ea7263716198cde745ca0c3bbdbd1b56","tid":1115792,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"賽事倒數網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marble-sports.com/hub/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marble-sports.com%2Fhub%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=4cd03f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.marble-sports.com/hub/</a>"},{"pid":"4e7c515c233c5465411806ac03b56e05687a6ef5","tid":1115792,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"做下賽前分析推po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今屆第一場嘅項目係Underwater Race，如果淨係睇名今屆有主場之利嘅 Oceanics 好似十分有優勢。但係根據 Oceanics 以往水中競賽嘅成績，通常都只係位居中下水平，唔知係咪因為咁所以今屆改咗賽道設計，由直路改為上下Z字形，但係顯然冇用，喺2019友誼賽嘅Underwater Race依然係排包尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同 Oceanics 相反，Midnight Wisps 雖然叫鬼火但係水中競賽成績出奇地好，喺2017年嘅 Underwater Race 獲得第一名，加上係2018冬奧總冠軍綜合能力無疑相當出色，十分值得關注。<br />\n<br />\n而 Savage Speeders 係競速項目嘅傳統勁旅，但係水中競速嘅表現十分兩極，一係最top一係最尾，唔知今次賽道改動對佢地嘅表現如何?"},{"pid":"6c41331592fd437db9aa2f442dfbaf0dc8199c26","tid":1115792,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"推，波子有無規格限制"},{"pid":"16738590f18db36eb339b29bfa46fa9062b39631","tid":1115792,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"